    "\"%@\" is using the USB connection to the device, so the phone can't be reached. Quit it, then rescan." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"%@\" is using the USB connection to the device, so the phone can't be reached. Quit it, then rescan."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「%@」正在使用與裝置的 USB 連線，因此無法連上手機。請結束它後重新掃描。"
          }
        }
      }
