    "Quit \"%@\" and Rescan" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Quit \"%@\" and Rescan"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "結束「%@」並重新掃描"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When on, the current folder is checked every few seconds, so files added or removed on the phone show up automatically. A shorter interval keeps the list fresher, but the check shares the USB connection with file transfers and may occasionally delay the start of a transfer for a moment. When off, changes reported by the phone still appear, and you can always refresh manually from the toolbar." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "When on, the current folder is checked every few seconds, so files added or removed on the phone show up automatically. A shorter interval keeps the list fresher, but the check shares the USB connection with file transfers and may occasionally delay the start of a transfer for a moment. When off, changes reported by the phone still appear, and you can always refresh manually from the toolbar."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "開啟後，每隔幾秒會檢查一次目前資料夾，手機端新增或移除的檔案就會自動出現在列表中。間隔越短，列表越即時，但這項檢查與檔案傳輸共用同一條 USB 連線，偶爾可能讓傳輸晚一點才開始；間隔越長則越省資源。關閉後，手機主動回報的變動仍會顯示，也隨時可以從工具列手動重新整理。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
