    "When on, the current folder is checked every few seconds, so files added or removed on the phone show up automatically. A shorter interval keeps the list fresher, but the check shares the USB connection with file transfers and may occasionally delay the start of a transfer for a moment. When off, changes reported by the phone still appear, and you can always refresh manually from the toolbar." : {

